### Context

I create this dataset to increase the data existing on another dataset I am working on https://www.kaggle.com/gregorut/videogamesales


### Content

The console.csv has a console list with its manufacturers and sales. From: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_best-selling_game_consoles
I made color.csv for practice reasons, it is a file assigning colors to manufacturers for plotting.
The region file refers to the regions in https://www.kaggle.com/gregorut/videogamesales , I am just assigning colors for plot.
